ALC_Reasoner

Class JumpingTableau

  • java.lang.Object
    • ALC_Reasoner.ChronologicalTableau
      • ALC_Reasoner.JumpingTableau
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tableau
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LOGJumpingTableau

    public class JumpingTableau
extends ChronologicalTableau
    The type Jumping tableau. as suggested by the name this is the implementation of the tableau which makes use of the Jumpig (or BackJumping) Backtrack as described in the chapther 3.5 of the "Efficient and generic reasoning for modal logics", Z.Li, 2008.
    See Also:
    Efficient and generic reasoning for modal logics
